title: AI Consensus
subtitle: What makes IndiaAGI different from ChatGPT? ChatGPT gives you one answer based on what it knows. IndiaAGI brings together five AIs — DeepSeek, ChatGPT, Gemini, Claude, and Grok — who debate and agree on the best answer after 3 rounds. It's the only place where AIs work together instead of competing. Want to see how it works? Just click "Explore Now."
